    "## Joint and conditional probabilities\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Fundamental Rule\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ \n",
    "P(A,B) = P(A|B) P(B)\\\\\n",
    "P(A, B | C) = P(A|B, C) P(B|C)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Chain Rule\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "P(A_1, A_2, A_3, ..., A_n) = P(A_1|A_2, A_3, ..., A_n) P(A_2|A_3, ..., A_n) ... P(A_n)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
